    public interface ISomeipTpChannel

    ISomeipTpChannel: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    This element is used to assign properties to SomeipTpConnections that are referencing this SomeipTpChannel.

        double getRxTimeoutTime()
        Query the value of the attribute RxTimeoutTime.

        The value or null
